QuestData.Title: No Problem Tar Can't Solve
QuestData.Description:
I'm not going to lie... I did wicked things in my youth and I've been living with de shame ever since.
But Zaluto is going to die without my healing, and we're all going to die if dat dino isn't taken care of.
Dere is a lot of tar in dis area. I need it to cure Zaluto of whatever is infecting him here.
Get me dat tar, and I'll be able to save Zaluto from dis fate.
